2. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses strategies for deploying smart services over different territories, which involves control and management of systems. 
3. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper discusses parallel and distributed simulation techniques, which are related to distributed computing. 
4. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper discusses agent-based simulation techniques, which are related to multiagent systems. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper discusses adaptive simulation techniques, which are related to artificial intelligence.
